    "# SMIRK – 3D Facial Expression Reconstruction (CVPR 2024) — Lightning.ai\n",
    "\n",
    "**Paper:** [SMIRK: 3D Facial Expressions Through Analysis-by-Neural-Synthesis](https://arxiv.org/abs/2404.04104)  \n",
    "**Repo:** https://github.com/georgeretsi/smirk  \n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook runs **image inference** using the pretrained SMIRK model on Lightning.ai Studios.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Before running\n",
    "1. **Enable GPU** — In your Studio, click the machine selector at the top and choose a GPU machine (e.g. T4 or A10G).\n",
    "2. **HF Token** — Set your Hugging Face token in Cell 5. The FLAME model downloads automatically from a private HF dataset (no manual upload needed).\n",
    "\n",
    "All other dependencies are downloaded automatically."
   ]
  },
